sentences: In 2002 Citi has broken up and Lex has founded Mechanical Poet.
In 2007 Plotnikoff was offered to compose several soundtracks for video games developed by Akella.

In 2010 he released his new electronic music work called Hattifatteners roughly based on the Moomin series by Tove Jansson and started an industrial music project 'Luna Damien' with one of the ex-Mechanical Poet singers Jerry Lenin.
In 2014 Lex started an electronic rock project called Last Fighter.
The debut album 'Neon Children' was released on February 27, 2017.
